descript.abstract:
Brief narrative of the data set: These data are derived from a correction using heads-up digitization of the original ssnerr_boundary_utm10-wgs84.shp file. Original was not accurate especially on the SSNERR west boundary. The correction is not yet complete- north boundary through Day Creek inlet and down the upper east side need to be verified.
Base Map: Coos County real color aerial photo, 0.5 meter resolution. Scale used during digitization was approximately 1:2,250.
Criteria used: Based on 1991 admin boundary survey maps updated using Coos County taxlot shapefile.
Method: Boundary was created on an electronic map (ArcMap 9.2) by using heads-up digitizing.
Resolution used to delineate the boundary on electronic map: NA
descript.purpose: Correction of the ssnerr_boundary_utm10-wgs84.shp file. Updates to the SSNERR adminiatrative boundary.
